{"comments":"Shape — Tensor shape molecule composed of dimension atoms.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nA tensor shape is an ordered list of dimensions. Shape algebra enables:\n- Broadcasting compatibility checks\n- Reshape validation (total elements must match)\n- Shape inference for operations\n\n## Diffusion Model Context\n\nCommon shapes in diffusion models:\n- Image: [batch, channels, height, width] (NCHW)\n- Latent: [batch, 4, h/8, w/8]\n- Attention: [batch, heads, seq, seq] or [batch, seq, embed]\n- Text embed: [batch, 77, 768] or [batch, 77, 1024]\n\n## Invariants\n\n- All dimensions are >= 1 (enforced by Dim)\n- Shape with zero dimensions is scalar\n- Shape algebra preserves element count where required\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Prelude (Eq, Ord, Show)\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Tensor.Dimension (Dim, DimExpr)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Dimension"],"Dim"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Shape.purs","start":[154,15]},"title":"Shape"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Shape"],"Shape"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[156,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Tensor/Shape.purs","start":[156,1]},"title":"eqShape"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Tensor","Shape"],"Shape"],"tag":"